{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Cozy Creative Designs</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #A52A2A; /* Brownish-red for a cozy feel */\n            --secondary-color: #D2B48C; /* Tan, complements red without harsh contrast */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #F5F5DC; /* Beige for warmth */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n            padding-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        section:last-of-type {\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item img {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 3px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item div {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #8B0000; /* Darker red on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: auto; /* Pushes footer to the bottom */\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .service-item {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            .service-item img {\n                margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Cozy Creative Designs</h1>\n        <p>Crafting warm and inviting digital experiences.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>We are a small, passionate team of designers dedicated to creating beautiful, user-friendly, and memorable digital products. We believe in a collaborative and cozy approach, ensuring your vision comes to life in a comfortable and creative environment.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=UI\" alt=\"UI Design Icon\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>User Interface (UI) Design</h3>\n                    <p>Creating intuitive and aesthetically pleasing interfaces that delight your users.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=UX\" alt=\"UX Design Icon\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>User Experience (UX) Design</h3>\n                    <p>Mapping out seamless user journeys and ensuring your product is both functional and enjoyable.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Web\" alt=\"Web Design Icon\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Web Design & Development</h3>\n                    <p>Building responsive and engaging websites that reflect your brand's unique personality.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Our Work</h2>\n            <p>While we can't showcase everything here, we've helped businesses like yours shine online. We focus on quality over quantity, ensuring each project receives our full attention.</p>\n            <p><em>Visit our <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--brand-color); text-decoration: underline;\">portfolio page</a> for more details!</em></p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Let's Create Together</h2>\n            <p>Ready to bring your idea to life in a warm and collaborative space? Get in touch with us today!</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:hello@cozycreativedesigns.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Quote</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Cozy Creative Designs. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple script for potential future interactivity or animations\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            console.log('Cozy Creative Designs website loaded!');\n            // Could add scroll animations or hover effects here if needed\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}